<P>
 Dutch Coach Dick Advocaat tried to fake out the press -- and Irish spies -- 
when he switched to a conservative four-defender, four-midfielder, two-forward 
alignment in a scrimmage Saturday at the Florida Citrus Bowl. 
</P>
<P>
