<TEXT>
<P>
 David Letterman, on the possible merger of CBS Inc. and the QVC home shopping 
network: "The merger has not yet gone through, so do me a favor: Quit phoning 
in here trying to buy my hair piece." 
</P>
<P>
 Among Dave's Top 10 Least Popular Tourist Attractions: 
</P>
<P>
 * Six Flags Over Newark. 
</P>
<P>
 * The Magnificent Algae Forest of Willie Nelson's Bathtub. 
</P>
<P>
 * Sen. Packwood's House of Hands. 
</P>
<P>
 * The Regis De Milo. 
</P>
<P>
 * The Grand Ole Oprah. 
</P>
<P>
 * EuroDisney. 
</P>
